---
title: Falafel & Feta Salad Pita Wraps with Pickled Onion, Yogurt Sauce & Shawarma-Spiced Potatoes
description: We’re so excited about this spin on an all-time favorite sandwich! There’s fluffy pitas, a lemony yogurt sauce, and crispy chickpea falafel. It’s all garnished with a tomato, cuke, and feta salad and tangy pickled onion. A side of spice-roasted potato wedges makes this a hearty meal.
